Text: I just read this now, so it was weird for me to see in the other comics how they were already had the eight hammers. I was thinking, "when the hell did they defeat the Serpent?"
Lame is right, its why I stick to DC.

I like both DC and Marvel, but I prefer Marvel because of I've always known it. I'm only getting more acquainted with DC lately. Not a huge fan, but Lantern + Batman comics are very well written. Really like Batman comics. 

Care a lot less about Superman.
